{"tid":275937,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣西南寧阿叔地鐵站內表演企喺度大便","createTime":"2017-06-08T11:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T13:35:26.000Z","uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"298a30b58a5ab7e9dad483c0ded94500589ac872","tid":275937,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T11:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.nextmag.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170608/640_088aad4c1a6586ea93c02c15e2bf022f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.nextmag.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170608%2F640_088aad4c1a6586ea93c02c15e2bf022f.jpg&h=9bd72620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國廣西南寧一名男子，日前在當地的地鐵站內，在穿著長褲站立的情況下，竟然能夠便便，他「高超的技藝」獲得中港外媒體報導。<br />\n <br />\n根據《香港醬聞》報導，這名男子便便的過程，被監視器全程拍攝下來，影片還被傳到各個視頻網站。影片中，男子先是走到地鐵站內，比較沒有人經過的角落，無聲息地站著，然後見到一坨糞便，從他的褲管內滑出來、掉在地上。男子便便後離開，而這坨大便，則是留在原地給清掃阿姨收拾。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breakingnews/international/306966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nextmag.com.tw%2Fbreakingnews%2Finternational%2F306966&d=cDpCooU48CyrVJafXT1IonadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=b2520025\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breakingnews/international/306966</a><br />\n<br />\n支那網有片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://item.btime.com/35h129njaaq96lb05bl93s9l16n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fitem.btime.com%2F35h129njaaq96lb05bl93s9l16n&d=cDpCooU48CyrVJafXT1IonadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=54683523\" target=\"_blank\">http://item.btime.com/35h129njaaq96lb05bl93s9l16n</a>"},{"pid":"dd667ed440896d316c51642a591fd6ca2e5b9976","tid":275937,"uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:22:57.000Z","msg":"睇左做唐寧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49cd56b2eafdcd9298e5c3cb11012afb4a93bac4","tid":275937,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:3